OL,4,Chospital ward jailed
OL,6,FA woman who tried to kill her elderly
OL,7,Fmother on a hospital ward using
OL,8,Fpillows and a knife has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor three years.
OL,11,FSusan Hardwick, 65, told medical staff
OL,12,Fat Doncaster Royal Infirmary "I want
OL,13,Fto kill her" as they tried to drag her
OL,14,Foff Joan Hardwick, who was 89 at the
OL,15,Ftime, Sheffield Crown Court heard on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FStaff were able to restrain Hardwick
OL,19,Fand report the incident to police.
