OL,6,FHardwick's mother suffered a minor
OL,7,Finjury to her neck believed to have
OL,8,Fbeen caused by a small steak knife,
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire Police said.
OL,11,FA judge heard that Hardwick, who
OL,12,Fappeared in the dock using a
OL,13,Fwheelchair, later told staff her
OL,14,Fmother "had no quality of life", but
OL,15,Fprosecutors said Joan Hardwick was
OL,16,Fbeing prepared for discharge to a care
OL,17,Fhome, "was not at death's door" and
OL,18,F"has remained well since".
