OL,3,CWoman who tried to kill mum on
OL,4,Chospital ward jailed
OL,6,FHardwick, of Beech Road, Armthorpe,
OL,7,FDoncaster, admitted attempted murder
OL,8,Fat a previous hearing following a
OL,9,Flengthy process to decide whether she
OL,10,Fwas fit to plead.
OL,12,FThe defendant, who has cerebral palsy,
OL,13,Fand is thought to have a learning
OL,14,Fdisability, and who is being treated
OL,15,Ffor cancer, sobbed loudly throughout
OL,16,Fher sentencing and as she was wheeled
OL,17,Fout of the dock to begin her sentence.
